{"id":2881,"date":"2024-03-22T16:39:12","date_gmt":"2024-03-22T09:39:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2881"},"modified":"2024-03-22T16:39:12","modified_gmt":"2024-03-22T09:39:12","slug":"thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-nam-2024-nganh-giao-duc-hoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-nam-2024-nganh-giao-duc-hoc\/","title":{"rendered":"TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O TUY\u1ec2N SINH N\u0102M 2024 NG\u00c0NH GI\u00c1O D\u1ee4C H\u1eccC"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 n\u1eb1m trong Top c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng ASEAN (ASEAN 2024: AppliedHE). Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Qu\u1ed1c gia; \u0111\u1ea1t Ba sao v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Asean\u00a0(UPM).\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u0103m 2024, Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n sinh <strong>ng\u00e0nh <\/strong><strong>Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c h\u1ecdc<\/strong> <strong>chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 T\u00e2m l\u00fd h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng<\/strong>, nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>1. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong>: Th\u00ed sinh t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>2. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u00eau:<\/strong> 25<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>3. Th\u1eddi gian<\/strong> <strong>nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc:<\/strong> t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>15\/<\/strong><strong>0<\/strong><strong>4\/2024 &#8211; 15\/0<\/strong><strong>5\/2024.<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; T\u1eb7ng <strong>01 Laptop Samsung<\/strong> (tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 10.000.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/1 su\u1ea5t); <strong>Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed K\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1 trong 01 n\u0103m h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean<\/strong> tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 12.000.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/1 su\u1ea5t. Khi th\u00ed sinh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed 7.200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y 15\/05\/2024 <em>(S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f9 tr\u1eeb v\u00e0o h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed khi th\u00ed sinh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c)<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>4. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c <\/strong><strong>tuy\u1ec3n sinh: <\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u00ed sinh c\u00f3 Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfng Anh qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf (IELTS, TOEFL iBT, TOEIC v\u00e0 Cambridge) t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng <strong>IELTS t\u1eeb 5.0 tr\u1edf l\u00ean<\/strong> <em>(<a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/PHU-LUC-1_TBTS-Giao-duc-hoc-2024.pdf\">Ph\u1ee5 l\u1ee5c 1<\/a>);<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">&#8211; X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT v\u1edbi T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a K\u1ef3 1, 2 L\u1edbp 11 + K\u1ef3 1 l\u1edbp 12 <em>ho\u1eb7c<\/em> T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 c\u1ee7a 03 m\u00f4n trong t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n + \u0111i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb <strong>21,0<\/strong><strong> \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong> tr\u1edf l\u00ean;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>T<\/strong><strong>\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><em><strong>: <\/strong><\/em><strong>A00<\/strong> (To\u00e1n, L\u00fd, H\u00f3a); <strong>D01<\/strong> (To\u00e1n, V\u0103n, Ti\u1ebfng Anh).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>5<\/strong>. <strong>L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1eddi gian: <strong>3,5 <\/strong><strong>n\u0103m;<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng. Trong \u0111\u00f3 02 k\u1ef3 v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc v\u1eeba th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c\/doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" width=\"111\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-20720\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Untitled-2-01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"87\" height=\"87\" \/><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" width=\"106\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-18465 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Artboard-1-copy.png\" alt=\"Logo Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4\" width=\"79\" height=\"79\" \/><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" width=\"109\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-20722\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Untitled-2-04.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"68\" height=\"68\" \/><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" width=\"144\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-18537\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/Logo-REK-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"77\" height=\"77\" \/><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" width=\"98\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-20718\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Letco.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"84\" height=\"84\" \/><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center;\" width=\"108\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-20716\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/Isshin.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"92\" height=\"92\" \/><\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"111\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng TH &amp;THCS UNIGO<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"106\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"109\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng THPT Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"144\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Vi\u1ec7n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n giao tri th\u1ee9c<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"98\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f4ng ty Letco<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;\" width=\"108\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f4ng ty Nh\u1eadt ng\u1eef ISSHIN<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>6. C\u00e1c ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>6.1. H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc: <\/strong><\/span>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>T\u1eb7ng ngay <\/strong>100% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed n\u0103m th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eb7ng 100% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u00e1c n\u0103m h\u1ecdc k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp khi \u0111\u1ea1t <strong>tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 Ti\u1ebfng Anh <\/strong>t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng IELTS t\u1eeb <strong>5.0 <\/strong>tr\u1edf l\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0110i\u1ec3m Trung b\u00ecnh chung t\u00edch l\u0169y l\u1ea7n 1 \u0111\u1ea1t lo\u1ea1i Kh\u00e1 tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eb7ng 50% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u0103m k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp khi sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 Ti\u1ebfng Anh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng IELTS t\u1eeb <strong>4<\/strong>.<strong>5 <\/strong>v\u00e0 \u0110i\u1ec3m Trung b\u00ecnh chung t\u00edch l\u0169y l\u1ea7n 1 \u0111\u1ea1t lo\u1ea1i Trung b\u00ecnh;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p: Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng Th\u1ea1c s\u0129 t\u1ea1i <\/strong>c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>6.2. Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m: <\/strong>Cam k\u1ebft gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m sau t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc\/t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c\/doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>7<\/strong><strong>.<\/strong> <strong>H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 <\/strong><strong>x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p THPT (gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi), <\/span>h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1 THPT;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea3n sao CMND\/CCCD, gi\u1ea5y khai sinh, c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u01b0u ti\u00ean kh\u00e1c (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>8<\/strong><strong>. \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Km 15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1ch 2:\u00a0Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, t\u1ea1i:<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>W<\/strong><strong>ebsite:<\/strong><a href=\"http:\/\/www.tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\">www.tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn<\/a> ho\u1eb7c<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Fanpage: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\">https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Hotline<\/strong><strong>: <\/strong>0934.078.668 ho\u1eb7c 02433.861.601<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 n\u1eb1m trong Top c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng ASEAN (ASEAN 2024: AppliedHE). Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c Qu\u1ed1c gia; \u0111\u1ea1t Ba sao v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Asean\u00a0(UPM).\u00a0 N\u0103m 2024, Nh\u00e0 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":9,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36,20],"tags":[109,110,49,42,125],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2881"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/9"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2881"}],"version-histor